@baseUri = http://localhost:5222

### Clean up between runs if needed

DELETE {{baseUri}}/People/Tyrion HTTP/1.1

### Add a Person

POST {{baseUri}}/People/new HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Name" : "Tyrion"
}

### Now see that person

GET {{baseUri}}/People/Tyrion HTTP/1.1


